{"type":"message","id":"3c1fda0e","parentId":"5f2388d2","timestamp":"2026-04-17T12:08:24.353Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking \"怎么样\" (how is it going) and \"在吗\" (are you there). They seem to be checking if I'm still there or if the issue has been resolved. \n\nLooking at the conversation history:\n1. User asked about Minimax 2.7 not working\n2. I provided detailed diagnosis - API key is a placeholder\n3. User asked again the same question\n4. I provided a more concise answer\n5. Now user is asking \"怎么样\" and \"在吗\"\n\nThe user might be expecting me to help fix the issue. Let me check if there's anything I can do to help, or if they need to provide the API key.\n\nActually, I should respond to confirm I'm here and maybe offer to help update the config if they have the API key.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n在的。刚才已经诊断出Minimax M2.7无法使用的原因：\n\n**问题**：API密钥是占位符 `\"your-actual-minimax-key\"`，没有填入真实的密钥。\n\n**解决方案**：需要你提供真实的Minimax API密钥，我可以帮你更新配置。\n\n你现在有API密钥吗？如果有，告诉我即可帮你配置好。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":48319,"output":238,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48557,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776427694183,"responseId":"chatcmpl-c23abdfd-5fd6-4a71-a2fe-40749630c12c"}}
