{"type":"message","id":"b8ea3229","parentId":"91d93ea7","timestamp":"2026-04-17T12:11:59.774Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found it! The D:\\coam\\.openclaw\\.env file has the same placeholder MINIMAX_API_KEY. So the Minmax API key is not configured in the D:\\coam\\ setup either.\n\nThe user asked me to compare the two folders. The issue is:\n1. Current Linux setup (~/.openclaw/): has the API key in auth-profiles.json (minimax:cn with key sk-cp-...)\n2. D:\\coam\\.openclaw\\: the .env file still has the placeholder \"your-actual-minimax-key\"\n\nSo the D:\\coam\\ setup needs to be updated with the actual API key. Let me tell the user what I found and suggest they need to update the .env file in D:\\coam\\.openclaw\\ as well.\n\nBut wait - the user said they just updated it and it's still not working. Maybe they updated the wrong file or location? Or maybe the D:\\coam\\ is the Windows setup and they need to restart the Windows gateway?\n\nLet me ask for clarification or suggest next steps.","thinkingSignature":"03c1f661a54a88f5a8c66119539501eb46f89fd0bf9312c264139b678f582975"},{"type":"text","text":"找到问题了！对比两个配置：\n\n## 📊 对比结果\n\n| 项目 | D:\\coam\\.openclaw\\ (Windows) | ~/.openclaw (Linux) |\n|------|-------------------------------|---------------------|\n| **.env** | `MINIMAX_API_KEY=your-actual-minimax-key` (占位符) | - |\n| **auth-profiles.json** | 只有 `volcengine-plan` | 有 `minimax:cn` (已填入真实密钥) |\n| **Minimax M2.7 配置** | 有，但缺 API 密钥 | 有，且密钥已配置 |\n\n## 🔍 结论\n\nD:\\coam\\.openclaw\\ 的 `.env` 文件里 **API 密钥还是占位符**，没有更新。\n\n你之前更新的是 Linux 系统的配置 (`~/.openclaw/`)，但运行的可能是 Windows 系统 (`D:\\coam\\`)？\n\n## 🔧 解决方案\n\n需要把同样的密钥填到 `D:\\coam\\.openclaw\\.env`：\n\n```\nMINIMAX_API_KEY=sk-cp-TVuvlmq_fUfdvSwhbwPgAxgFoBCtPc1acKznw8MU2HeWtkWozK3ruBwFLNV2YKdlaYI5BCuiqQnWaI_kB6rmyrYw37SYXtIR1th4i71CR82WvLFT2kKZ_Ls\n```\n\n或者告诉我你现在用的是哪个系统运行的 OpenClaw？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":36281