{"type":"message","id":"0cf10880","parentId":"782fd06c","timestamp":"2026-04-17T12:14:08.628Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"openclaw.json was modified at 18:55 (6:55 PM today), which is very recent - about 1 hour before the user's messages.\n\nLet me now summarize my comprehensive analysis. The key findings are:\n\n1. **D:\\coam\\.openclaw** has these issues:\n   - `.env` file still has placeholder `MINIMAX_API_KEY=your-actual-minimax-key`\n   - `openclaw.json` was recently modified (18:55 today)\n   - The default model in `openclaw.json` is `codingplan/minimax-m2.5`, NOT M2.7\n   - `models.json` for minimax provider references `MINIMAX_API_KEY` env var (which is placeholder in .env)\n   - BUT `auth-profiles.json` has the real key stored in `minimax:cn` profile\n   - `auth-state.json` shows `minimax:cn` was successfully used recently (errorCount: 0, lastUsed is recent)\n\n2. **The key problem**: \n   - The `models.json` minimax provider has `\"apiKey\": \"MINIMAX_API_KEY\"` which refers to env var\n   - But the env var in `.env` is still the placeholder\n   - However, auth-state shows minimax is working - this suggests OpenClaw might be reading from auth-profiles.json instead of the env var in some cases\n\n3. **Why might it not work?**\n   - The .env file may not be loaded/refreshed\n   - The openclaw.json agent config might be overriding the model selection\n   - The user might need to restart OpenClaw to pick up the new auth-profiles.json\n\n4. **What needs to be done**:\n   - Update .env file with the real API key OR\n   - Make sure OpenClaw reads from auth-profiles.json correctly\n   - Potentially restart OpenClaw to reload configuration\n\nLet me provide a comprehensive analysis to the user.","thinkingSignature":"548419a7daa1c0f16a0fcc7e67b382d7b7bb31b573fa13a1260336104501b689"},{"type":"text","text":"好，全面分析 D:\\coam\\.openclaw 配置：\n\n## 📊 D:\\coam\\.openclaw 完整分析\n\n### 1️⃣ 关键配置状态\n\n| 文件 | 状态 | 问题 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `.env` | ❌ 占位符 | `MINIMAX_API_KEY=your-actual-minimax-key` |\n| `auth-profiles.json` | ✅ 已填入真实密钥 | `minimax:cn` 已有正确密钥 |\n| `models.json` | ⚠️ 引用方式有问题 | minimax provider 用 `\"apiKey\": \"MINIMAX_API_KEY\"` (env引用) |\n| `openclaw.json` | 🔄 刚修改过 | 18:55 刚保存 |\n\n### 2️⃣ 核心问题：API Key 引用链断裂\n\n```\nmodels.json 中:  \"apiKey\": \"MINIMAX_API_KEY\"\n                      ↓\n              读取 .env 文件\n                      ↓\n              .env 中是占位符！\n```\n\n**但是** `auth-profiles.json` 里已经有真实密钥了！\n\n```\nauth-profiles.json:  minimax:cn → sk-cp-TVuvlmq_fUfdvSwhbwPg... (真实密钥)\n```\n\nOpenClaw 应该优先用 auth-profiles，但 models.json 的 env 引用可能覆盖了这个逻辑。\n\n### 3️⃣ 默认模型配置\n\n`openclaw.json` 中：\n```json\n\"agents\": {\n  \"defaults\": {\n    \"model\": {\n      \"primary\": \"codingplan/minimax-m2.5\"  // ← 默认是 M2.5，不是 M2.7！\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n所以系统默认用的是 **M2.5**，不是 M2.7！\n\n### 4️⃣ auth-state 显示实际使用情况\n\n```json\n\"minimax:cn\": {\n  \"errorCount\": 0,           // ✅ 无错误\n  \"lastUsed\": 1776351784135, // ✅ 最近使用过\n  \"lastFailureAt\": 1776329668400  // 之前的失败，已恢复\n}\n```\n\n**Minimax 实际可用！** 只是在用 M2.5 而不是 M2.7。\n\n### 5️⃣ .env 文件必须更新\n\n即使 auth-profiles.json 有密钥，models.json 的 provider 级配置可能还是读 env：\n\n```\nMINIMAX_API_KEY=这里要填真实密钥\n```\n\n## 🔧 解决方案\n\n**方案 A**：更新 `.env` 文件\n```\nMINIMAX_API_KEY=sk-cp-TVuvlmq_fUfdvSwhbwPgAxgFoBCtPc1acKznw8MU2HeWtkWozK3ruBwFLNV2YKdlaYI5BCuiqQnWaI_kB6rmyrYw37SYXtIR1th4i71CR82WvLFT2kKZ_Ls\n```\n\n**方案 B**：修改 `models.json` 直接嵌入密钥\n```json\n\"minimax\": {\n  \"apiKey\": \"sk-cp-TVuvlmq_fUfdvSwhbwPgAxgFoBCtPc1acKznw8MU2HeWtkWozK3ruBwFLNV2YKdlaYI5BCuiqQnWaI_kB6rmyrYw37SYXtIR1th4i71CR82WvLFT2kKZ_Ls\"\n}\n```\n\n**方案 C**：如果想用 M2.7，需要改 openclaw.json 的默认模型：\n```json\n\"primary\": \"minimax/MiniMax-M2.7\"\n```\n\n## ❓ 需要确认\n\n1. 你想让哪个模型成为默认？M2.5 还是 M2.7？\n2. 要我帮你更新 .env 文件吗？\n\n需要我直接帮你修复吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":41694,"output":1219,"cacheRead":20856,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63769,"